  "prompt": "Who makes Clevo laptops?",
  "response": "Clevo laptops are manufactured by Clevo, a Taiwanese company that specializes in producing laptop computers, barebone laptop kits, and related components. As an original design manufacturer (ODM), Clevo provides the foundational hardware for various brand-name laptop sellers who may customize and rebrand these laptops for sale under their own labels. Some of these brands include Sager, Eurocom, Schenker, XMG, Eluktronics, and others.",
